The SileroVADConfig dataclass defines the configurable detection parameters. sampling_rate is no longer a config field (stage 8): the input is model-ready audio whose rate the upstream ffmpeg convert owns; the tool reads the actual rate from the file and validates it is one Silero supports (8k/16k).




def SileroVADConfig(
    threshold:float=0.5, min_speech_duration_ms:int=250, min_silence_duration_ms:int=100, speech_pad_ms:int=30,
    use_onnx:bool=True
)-&gt;None:

Configuration for Silero VAD parameters.

